ResponseMessages.QuickReplyTitle: qrm-roundtable

TextItems: RoundTable is the easiest way to start an asynchronous discussion for free and connect with the user through our global community!
RoundTable is a discussion platform designed to connect people from all over the world and help them easily share knowledge and grow.

The name of RoundTable comes from King Arthur's famed table in the Arthurian legend, around which he and his knights congregate. As the name suggests, it has no head, which means that everyone sitting there has the same status. Therefore, the RoundTable is a form of academic discussion. Participants agree on specific topics for discussion and debate. Everyone has an equal right to participate.

ResponseMessages.QuickReplyTitle: The discussion exploration page can be accessed directly from the navigation bar. Rising topics and popular discussion posts can be found there. Use it to see other hot topics everyone is discussing.

The discussion search page can be accessed directly from the navigation bar. You can search for discussion posts by entering the discussion title or topic keywords. Not only that, you can also find users through the search function.

You first need to log in to the platform before you can edit your profile details. The Edit Profile button can be seen on the profile page, which can be accessed by clicking the profile picture on the navigation bar.
After registering for a RoundTable account, you can log in by clicking the login button located at the bottom of the navigation bar. You may use a variety of features after logging in.

In order to use most of the features on RoundTable, you need to register for an account first. Just click the login button on the navigation bar, and then click the sign up text on the login screen. Your name, unique username, email and password are required to complete the registration process
You can opt out at any time after logging in. Just navigate to your profile page and scroll down, then you will see a red logout button at the bottom of the page.

If you forget your password or need an enhanced password, you definitely need to change your password. First, navigate to the login page. Then, click the Forgot Password button. Enter your username and updated password twice. Click the Get Code button, and a six-digit code will be sent to the email used to register the account.

Then, click the Forgot Password button. Enter your username and updated password twice. Click the Get Code button, and a six-digit code will be sent to the email used to register the account.
